放到 `components` 文件夹下（可能有违 `components` 这个文件夹的定义，我的理解是 `components` 用来存放一些复用性很高的组件，而不是这种零散的对话框单组件文件）所以就导致我现在的项目结构很多 `xxxDialog.vue` 文件，既不知道如何归类存放，也不知道该怎么高效复用。","content_rendered":"<p>前端基于 Vue3 + Element Plus + Vite + TypeScript 。当前，每个页面都有类似于：详情对话框、编辑对话框和各种嵌套对话框等，该复用的已经复用过了，剩下的对话框都含有各自的特色内容，不宜复用，强行复用可能会导致单文件代码量过多不利于后期维护。</p>\n<p><strong>目前的疑问</strong>：我现在的做法是拆分每个 <code>el-dialog</code> 为单文件组件，存放到 <code>components</code> 文件夹下（可能有违 <code>components</code> 这个文件夹的定义，我的理解是 <code>components</code> 用来存放一些复用性很高的组件，而不是这种零散的对话框单组件文件）所以就导致我现在的项目结构很多 <code>xxxDialog.vue</code> 文件，既不知道如何归类存放，也不知道该怎么高效复用。</p>\n","last_modified":1701575011,"replies":41,"id":997210},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":212955,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":4042,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":624594,"username":"username321","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/username321","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0c95fa472e7d2861a0d031dcdf01dd17?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0c95fa472e7d2861a0d031dcdf01dd17?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0c95fa472e7d2861a0d031dcdf01dd17?s=73&d=retro","created":1681745330,"last_modified":1681745330},"last_reply_by":"clementewy","last_touched":1701582761,"title":"那些听本地音乐的人，是从哪里下载的音乐？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/997213","created":1701573392,"deleted":0,"content":"","content_rendered":"","last_modified":1701573392,"replies":32,"id":997213},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/68d3/0a95/84_large.png?